Dol-ikyeobomyeon ama sijag-eun
2012 animyeon 13jjeum
Keundongwa dongsie wass-eo big problems
Yejeon-ui salmgwan hwagsilhi daleun

Salm-i nal gidaligo iss-eossne
Eolil jeogbuteo tain-ui siseon-e
Nochul-i doegi silh-eohaessji but geuleon naegeseo
Daleun nal kkeul-eonaessne gyesog. so I think I had it comin'

Achimmada seogangdaegyo geonneo yeouido
Chulgeunhaneun salm, inteobyu huen gong-yeon-i tto
Geuligo alcohol, kkeut-eobs-i naessdeon gog
Hangsang mwonga-e chwihae iss-eossne
Couldn't make sense of my life as a whole

Hyangsu, whisky, michin bam, the morning after
Radio, yeongi jaughan club-ui so-eum-e tto
Blackout, yeol si allam-e
Nun tteugo dasi syawo, keopiwa dambae

Gieog-i huimihae jinan bam
Mwonga-e chwihan chae jinagan
Sigandeul ije geuman
